<p>Hello <%= @resource.name %>,</p>

<p>Someone has requested a link to change your passphrase, and you can do this through the link below.</p>

<p><%= link_to 'Change my passphrase', edit_password_url(@resource, :reset_password_token => @resource.reset_password_token) %></p>

<p>If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.</p>
<p>Your passphrase won't change until you access the link above and create a new one.</p>
<p>The link will be valid for 6 hours and will only work once.</p>
